{"tid":794223,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"死侍2 Deadpool2","createTime":"2018-08-26T05:15:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-26T09:09:29.000Z","uid":9838,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"90c541e0c8162c9252d50b9c84639ae38df625b3","tid":794223,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T05:15:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://movie.eservice-hk.net/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/d62b60b0050162088a6d1e134b009b9c-728x1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmovie.eservice-hk.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F08%2Fd62b60b0050162088a6d1e134b009b9c-728x1024.jpg&h=45593218&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n導演 : 大衛雷奇<br />\n演員 : 賴恩尼諾斯, 佐斯布連<br />\n片長 : 2小時<br />\n級別 : III 級<br />\n語言 : 英語 (中文字幕)<br />\n上映 : 15.5.2018 (公映)<br />\n<br />\n故事簡介<br />\n萬眾期待MARVEL年度玩嘢「屌」爆鉅製《死侍2》(DEADPOOL 2) ，由「二十世紀福斯影片」強勢發行，這個最反傳統、寸寸貢的超級英雄，經過上集票房口碑雙贏後，越來越大支嘢，自然越殺越高潮！賤嘴型男賴恩尼諾斯再度瞓身飾演的死侍，為了拯救一名死肥仔細路，不惜吹個靚雞班齊老友，聯同一眾年輕異變人、包括爆炸頭烈女多米諾等組成的超勁團隊「變種部隊」，晒冷出盡奶力，對抗來自未來、鍾意四圍炸的超級士兵機堡。死侍一邊打大佬一邊探索人生朋友愛人相處等大大大哲理（下删五百字），最重要當然是思考超級英雄的真意義 &mdash; 為對的事而戰，污糟邋遢在所難免！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/26/004848_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F004848_f753c3a75140ef4445b7e6826161c842.png&h=5b0ef3b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">遊客，如果您要查看本帖隱藏內容請回覆</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45824cbf4ebb354b35e9e558c23d0533e3d19141","tid":794223,"uid":69235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T07:23:18.000Z","msg":"係咪完整版黎<br />\n<br />\n有d位戲院睇果時無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10b083a45c4d654bc1f6b102d01de4513683b91","tid":794223,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45824cbf4ebb354b35e9e558c23d0533e3d19141","tid":794223